snippet.title: Johnny Depp Speaks On Defeating Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Is it true that Johnny Depp just defeated Amber Heard? 

Fans of Johnny Depp should rejoice: the actor is one step closer to winning his high-profile defamation case against ex-wife Amber Heard, and he is now determined to prove that Amber lied when she accused him of domestic violence in her infamous 2018 Washington Post op-ed.

However, we've heard that Johnny is concerned that Hollywood has already blacklisted him and that his career will never recover. 

So, what's the latest on Johnny and Amber's legal squabble? Will Johnny be able to prove his innocence at long last? Will Hollywood welcome him back if he does?
